in=31&order=position |title=United States Hot Dance Club Songs Best of the Decade |work=Billboard (Nielsen Business Media) |accessdate=14 August 2010}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align: center;\"|33\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n== Certifications ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"| Country\n!scope=\"col\"| Provider\n!scope=\"col\"| [[list of music recording sales certifications|Certification]]\n|-\n| Australia\n|[[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]]\n|2\u00d7  Platinum<ref name=\"AUS Cert\">{{cite web\n|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/httpwww.aria.com.aupageshttpwww.aria.com.auSINGLEaccreds2011.htm\n|title=ARIA Single Accreditations for 2011 |publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association|ARIA]] |work=ARIA Accreditations |year=2009 |accessdate=17 July 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| Austria\n|[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]]\n|2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"AUT Cert\">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.at/?section=goldplatin |title=Gold & Platin |language=German |publisher=I[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]] |work=ifpi.at |date=30 September 2009 |accessdate=9 August 2010 |at=''Search by title, enter \"When Love Takes Over\"'' |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nDfynkk6?url=http://www.ifpi.at/?section=goldplatin |archivedate=1 February 2010 }}</ref>\n|-\n| Belgium\n|IFPI\n|Gold<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/certifications.asp?year=2009 |title=Goud en Platina \u2013 Singles |language=Dutch |publisher=IFPI |work=[[Ultratop|ultratop.be]] |year=2009 |accessdate=9 August 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| Canada\n|[[Canadian Recording Industry Association|CRIA]]\n|Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cria.ca/gold/0909_g.php |title=Gold & Platinum Certification |publisher=[[Canadian Recording Industry Association|CRIA]] |work=cria.ca |year=2009 |accessdate=9 August 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101019173407/http://cria.ca/gold/0909_g.php 