promusicae.es |year=2009 |accessdate=9 August 2010}}</ref>\n|-\n| Switzerland\n|IFPI\n|Platinum<ref name=\"SW Cert\">{{cite web |url=http://swisscharts.com/awards.asp?year=2009 |title=Swiss Certifications by Year |publisher=IFPI / Hung Medien |work=Swisscharts.com |year=2009 |accessdate=17 July 2010 |language=de}}</ref>\n|-\n|United Kingdom\n|[[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]\n|Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/kelly-rowlands-official-top-10-biggest-songs__29487/|title=Kelly Rowland's Official Top 10 biggest songs|last=Myers|first=Justin|date=April 17, 2020|work=[[Official Charts Company]]|access-date=April 17, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Format\n! scope=\"col\" | Date\n! scope=\"col\" | Label\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Compact disc|CD]] single (2-track)<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n| 11 May 2009\n| rowspan=\"9\"| {{hlist|[[Virgin Records|Virgin France]]|[[EMI|EMI Music]]}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Music download|Digital download]]<ref name=\"Behind the Music\"/><ref name=\"Arie L\"/>\n| 10 June 2009\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| CD single (3-track)<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 12 June 2009\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Maxi single]]<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| France [[Gramophone record|12\"]] maxi single (1)<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n| 15 June 2009\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK 12\" maxi single (1)<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n| 22 June 2009\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK 12\" maxi single (2)<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n| 26 June 2009\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| France 12\" maxi single (2)<ref name=\"sc_Belgium (Wallonia)_David Guetta feat. Kelly Rowland\"/>\n| 31 July 2009\n|-\n! scope=\"r